                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " Maintain clear documentation for the view, including its purpose, dependencies, and any business rules applied. This will aid in maintenance and future enhancements."
